
1.Set myName to a string equal to your name and build myStr with myName between the strings My name is and and I am well!

code:
const myName = "Rabbit";
const myStr = "My name is" + myName + "and I am well!";

value: My name is Rabbit and I am well!



2.Appending Variables to Strings

code:
const anAdjective = "awesome!";
let ourStr = "freeCodeCamp is ";
ourStr += anAdjective;

value: ourStr would have the value freeCodeCamp is awesome!.
